milestones.description: Henry Osinde has broken the record for most ducks (4) in ODIs for CAN, going past de Groot's 3
Ashish Bagai has scored 7 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for CAN breaking John Davison's record
Dhaniram has become the top wicket-taker for CAN in ODIs with 33 wickets, going past John Davison's 31

stories.title: Debutant Foggo stars in Bermuda's three-wicket win
stories.subTitle: Canada v Bermuda, 1st ODI, King City
stories.summary: Bermuda took the lead in the three-match ODI series after beating Canada by three wickets in a closely-fought game, reduced by rain to 36 overs a side, at the Maple Leaf North-West Ground in King City
